      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RATTLER (4) was game in defeat off a low draw at the latest outing, finishing second and beaten 0.6 lengths (30.01) behind Captain Easy at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Overdue and is among the main hopes. LEKTRA JIMMY (2) was out of the placings last time when fifth at Horsham (27.69) but did record best time of the card when winning five back. Key runner on best form. JAZZY HOPE (1) finished in the minors last time but only a few starts back broke the clock when winning over 545m at Ballarat, taking a Grade 5 in a blistering 30.83. Top win three back and rates a key player again. IT'S LATE (7) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
